<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">Or (Param&egrave;tre Put graphique)</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	Param&egrave;tre de la d&eacute;claration graphique <tt><a href="KeyPgPutgraphics.html">Put</a></tt> qui utilise la manipulation de bits <tt><a href="KeyPgOpOr.html">Or</a></tt> comme m&eacute;thode de transformation image<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<b>Put</b> [ <i>target</i>, ] [ STEP ] ( <i>x</i>,<i>y</i> ), <i>source</i> [ ,( <i>x1</i>,<i>y1</i> )-( <i>x2</i>,<i>y2</i> ) ], <b>Or</b><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&egrave;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><b>Or</b></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">Obligatoire.<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
La m&eacute;thode <tt><b>Or</b></tt> combine chaque pixel source avec chaque pixel correspondant de la destination, en utilisant la fonction de manipulation de bits <tt><a href="KeyPgOpOr.html">Or</a></tt>.  Le r&eacute;sultat est renvoy&eacute; comme pixel destination.<br \>
Cette m&eacute;thode fonctionne dans tous les modes graphiques.  Il n'y a pas de masque de couleur, donc les valeurs de couleur de <tt>0</tt> (<tt><a href="KeyPgRgba.html">RGBA</a>(0, 0, 0, 0)</tt> en modes pleine couleur) n'auront aucun effet, en raison du comportement de <tt><a href="KeyPgOpOr.html">Or</a></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
En mode pleine couleur, chaque composante (rouge, vert, bleu et alpha) est conserv&eacute;e dans un ensemble discret de bits, ainsi l'op&eacute;ration peut affecter seulement certains canaux, en s'assurant que toutes les valeurs des autres canaux sont mises &agrave; <tt>0</tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="com">''Ouvre&nbsp;une&nbsp;fenetre&nbsp;graphique</span><br />
<span class="key">ScreenRes</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">320</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">200</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">16</span><br />
<br />
<span class="com">''Cree&nbsp;3&nbsp;sprites&nbsp;contenant&nbsp;cercles&nbsp;rouges,&nbsp;verts&nbsp;et&nbsp;bleus</span><br />
<span class="key">Const</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Integer</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">32</span><br />
<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Any</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Ptr</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cr</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cg</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cb</span><br />
<span class="wrd">cr</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">ImageCreate</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGBA</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">))</span><br />
<span class="wrd">cg</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">ImageCreate</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGBA</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">))</span><br />
<span class="wrd">cb</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">ImageCreate</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">*</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">2</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">+</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGBA</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">))</span><br />
<span class="key">Circle</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cr</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGB</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">255</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">f</span><br />
<span class="key">Circle</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cg</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGB</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">255</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">f</span><br />
<span class="key">Circle</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cb</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">RGB</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">0</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">255</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">1</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">f</span><br />
<br />
<span class="com">''Put&nbsp;le&nbsp;sprite&nbsp;avec&nbsp;trois&nbsp;niveaux&nbsp;multiplieur</span><br />
<span class="com">''differents,&nbsp;se&nbsp;recouvrant&nbsp;dans&nbsp;le&nbsp;milieu</span><br />
<span class="key">Put</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">146</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">108</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cr</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Or</span><br />
<span class="key">Put</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">174</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">108</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cg</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Or</span><br />
<span class="key">Put</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">(</span><span class="num">160</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="num">84</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">-</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">r</span><span class="oth">),</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">cb</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Or</span><br />
<br />
<span class="com">''Libere&nbsp;la&nbsp;memoire&nbsp;utilisee&nbsp;par&nbsp;les&nbsp;sprites</span><br />
